#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn23.46"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn23.46:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 23 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 23 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.46:0.2"
msgid "4. Upanisinnavagga "
msgstr "4. Sitting Close "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn23.46:0.3"
msgid "46. Nirodhadhammasutta "
msgstr "46. Liable To Cease "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn23.46:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.46:1.2"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho āyasmantaṃ rādhaṃ bhagavā etadavoca: "
msgstr "When Venerable Rādha was seated to one side, the Buddha said to him: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.46:1.3"
msgid "“yo kho, rādha, nirodhadhammo; tatra te chando pahātabbo, rāgo pahātabbo, chandarāgo pahātabbo. "
msgstr "“Rādha, you should give up any desire, any greed, any desire and greed for whatever is liable to cease. "

msgctxt "sn23.46:1.4"
msgid "Ko ca, rādha, nirodhadhammo? "
msgstr "And what is liable to cease? "

msgctxt "sn23.46:1.5"
msgid "Rūpaṃ kho, rādha, nirodhadhammo; tatra te chando pahātabbo, rāgo pahātabbo, chandarāgo pahātabbo. "
msgstr "Form is liable to cease. You should give up any desire, any greed, any desire and greed for it. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.46:1.6"
msgid "Vedanā … pe … "
msgstr "Feeling … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.46:1.7"
msgid "saññā … pe … "
msgstr "Perception … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.46:1.8"
msgid "saṅkhārā … pe … "
msgstr "Choices … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.46:1.9"
msgid "viññāṇaṃ nirodhadhammo; tatra te chando pahātabbo, rāgo pahātabbo, chandarāgo pahātabbo. "
msgstr "Consciousness is liable to cease. You should give up any desire, any greed, any desire and greed for it. "

msgctxt "sn23.46:1.10"
msgid "Yo kho, rādha, nirodhadhammo; tatra te chando pahātabbo, rāgo pahātabbo, chandarāgo pahātabbo”ti. "
msgstr "You should give up any desire, any greed, any desire and greed for whatever is liable to cease.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn23.46:1.11"
msgid "Upanisinnavaggo catuttho. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn23.46:2.1"
msgid "Māro ca māradhammo ca, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn23.46:2.2"
msgid "Aniccena apare duve; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn23.46:2.3"
msgid "Dukkhena ca duve vuttā, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn23.46:2.4"
msgid "Anattena tatheva ca; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn23.46:2.5"
msgid "Khayavayasamudayaṃ, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn23.46:2.6"
msgid "Nirodhadhammena dvādasāti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "sn23.46:2.7"
msgid "Rādhasaṃyuttaṃ samattaṃ. "
msgstr "The Linked Discourses with Rādha are complete."

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
